title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 §§ 43-2.1 - Scope

N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 §§ 43-2.1 - Scope

State Regulations

These regulations govern the application and eligibility determination process for the Uninsured Care Programs and establish the rights and responsibilities of applicants, participants, providers, and contractors in that process. Notes
